<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79adf11a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s3169"><num value="3169">§ 3169.</num><heading> Valid existing right of access</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this subchapter shall be construed to adversely affect any valid existing right of access.</p>
